{"id":123281,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/神奇铺砖机/","date":"2010-11-18T05:52:11Z","modified":"2010-11-18T05:52:11Z","title":"神奇铺砖机","content":"<p><p>来自: <a href=\"http://www.feedzshare.com/b/114794/2\">bullog.org &#8211; FeedzShare</a>  <a href=\"http://www.feedzshare.com/b/137/2\">煎蛋 &#8211; FeedzShare</a>  <a href=\"http://www.feedzshare.com/b/4580214/2\">中文热文榜|最新 &#8211; FeedzShare</a>  <br />\n<br />发布时间:2010年11月16日,  已有 9 人推荐 </p>\n<hr>\n<div>\n<p><img alt=\"http://jandan.net/\" src=\"http://pic.yupoo.com/jdvip/ACTJGlDZ/medium.jpg\" title=\"神奇铺砖机\" /></p>\n<p>街砖具备美观耐用的特性，但铺设的过程非常耗费人力物力。现在荷兰的 <a href=\"http://inhabitat.com/2010/11/15/amazing-brick-machine-rolls-out-roads-like-carpet/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tiger-Stone 铺砖机</a>可以大大减轻工人负担。铺砖机的原理在于精心设计的重力基础系统，只要把砖头堆放在砖斗上，通过的路面就会铺成一条最宽达到6米宽的完整砖路，非常省事方便。</p>\n<p>>>><a href=\"http://jandan.net/2010/11/16/amazing-brick-machine.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">继续浏览全文</a> &#8230;</p>\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"http://jandan.net/2010/11/16/amazing-brick-machine.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"本文链接\">©</a> 生抽 for <a href=\"http://jandan.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">煎蛋</a> / <a href=\"http://jandan.net/2010/11/16/amazing-brick-machine.html#comments\" rel=\"nofollow\">25条回复</a> / <a href=\"http://jandan.net/contribute\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"投稿通道\">投递</a> / 图片托管于<a href=\"http://v.yupoo.com/p/jdvip/?utm_source=jandan&#038;utm_medium=jandanlianjie&#038;utm_campaign=jandanrss\" rel=\"nofollow\">又拍网</a></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/1017243/tongji.gif\" /><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/997968/tongji.gif\" /></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}